                "invention-title": [
                    "Method for removing organic pollutants in wastewater by using chemical oxidation system converted by light-excited carbon dioxide",
                    "一种光激发二氧化碳转化的化学氧化体系去除废水有机污染物的方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention discloses a method for removing organic pollutants in wastewater by a chemical oxidation system for converting carbon dioxide through light excitation. The method comprises the following steps: introducing carbon dioxide into organic wastewater containing carbonate, and adding hydrogen peroxide under the irradiation of light with a specific wavelength to generate an oxidant bicarbonate peroxide. In the optical excitation process, pollutant molecules are converted into an excited state from a ground state, the reaction activity is remarkably improved, the energy of photons not only can directly photodecompose organic pollutants, but also can activate and decompose peroxybicarbonate to generate various active oxygen species, hydrogen peroxide can also be quickly activated and decomposed to generate hydroxyl radicals, and meanwhile, the activity of the photons is improved. The mass transfer rate of the system is improved by heat energy generated in the light energy irradiation process, so that organic pollutants in the wastewater are removed through synergistic oxidation. According to the system, under the action of optical excitation, the utilization rate of hydrogen peroxide and the yield of active oxygen species are improved by changing the reaction path of hydrogen peroxide, and the capability of oxidizing and removing organic pollutants in wastewater is remarkably improved."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明公开了一种光激发二氧化碳转化的化学氧化体系去除废水有机污染物的方法。该方法是将二氧化碳通入含有碳酸盐的有机废水中，在特定波长的光辐照下，加入过氧化氢，生成氧化剂过氧碳酸氢盐。在光激发过程中，污染物分子由基态转化为激发态，反应活性显著提高，光子的能量不但能够直接光解有机污染物，还可以活化分解过氧碳酸氢盐产生多种活性氧物种，过氧化氢也可被快速活化分解生成羟基自由基，同时，光能辐照过程中产生的热能提升体系的传质速率，从而协同增效的氧化去除废水有机污染物。该体系在光激发作用下，通过改变过氧化氢的反应路径来提高过氧化氢的利用率和活性氧物种的产率，显著提高了对废水有机污染物的氧化去除能力。"
                }
            ]
